            <header>
                <h3>Mobile Web CRM Proof of Concept</h3>
                <p>With this project, I was tasked with creating a working mobile web concept of our core CRM product to illustrate the benefits and drawbacks of responsive web solution when compared against an equilvalent native app. In total I had two weeks to design and develop a working prototype that was then presented to executive leadership.</p>
                <p>This exercise remains one of the largest accomplishments in my time at Total Expert thus far. In the end, the decision ultimately favored hiring a third party vendor to develop a native Android and iOS application. However, this proved that with minimal effort and resources it is possible to reengineer the designs and codebase of our existing platform to offer a more expansive mobile web solution. An initative that has already found footing in future planning.</p>

                <p><strong>Project Responsibilities</strong><br>UX/UI Design, Systems Engineer, Project Management, and Front-End Development</p>
